00:49:14,651 --> 00:49:16,949
- Reg?
- Go away.

725
00:49:18,689 --> 00:49:20,623
Reg, it's me, Brian.

726
00:49:20,691 --> 00:49:22,818
Get off!
Get off out of it!

727
00:49:22,893 --> 00:49:24,827
- Stan!
- Piss off.

728
00:49:24,895 --> 00:49:26,760
