731
00:49:32,002 --> 00:49:33,936
Coming.

732
00:49:34,004 --> 00:49:36,564
[Knocking Continues]

733
00:49:38,608 --> 00:49:42,339
[Preacher] Yea, verily at that time
it is written in the book of Obadiah,

734
