a man shall strike his donkey
and his nephew's donkey.

735
00:49:47,417 --> 00:49:50,284
[Continues, Indistinct]

736
00:49:50,354 --> 00:49:53,517
My eyes are dim.
I cannot see.

737
00:49:53,590 --> 00:49:56,058
- Are you Matthias?
- Yes.

738
