the People's Front of Judea.

740
00:50:02,366 --> 00:50:05,164
Me? No.
I'm just a poor old man.

741
00:50:05,235 --> 00:50:07,226
I have no time
for lawbreakers.

742
00:50:07,304 --> 00:50:09,636
My legs are grey.
My ears are nulled.

743
00:50:09,706 --> 00:50:11,731
My eyes are old and bent.

744
00:50:11,808 --> 00:50:13,867
Quiet!
Silly person.

745
00:50:13,944 --> 00:50:16,037
Guards, search the house.

746
00:50:16,113 --> 00:50:18,581
[Clattering]

