00:50:41,738 --> 00:50:43,968
Well, you could be stabbed.

754
00:50:44,041 --> 00:50:47,533
Stabbed? Takes a second.
Crucifixion lasts hours.

755
00:50:47,611 --> 00:50:50,205
It's a slow, horrible death.

756
00:50:50,280 --> 00:50:53,443
Well, at least it gets you
out in the open air.

757
00:50:54,718 --> 00:50:56,652
You're weird.

758
00:50:56,720 --> 00:50:59,655
[Clattering]

759
00:51:03,927 --> 00:51:07,226
No, sir.
Couldn't find anything, sir.

760
00:51:07,297 --> 00:51:11,529
Well, don't worry.
You've not seen the last of us, weirdo.

761
00:51:11,601 --> 00:51:14,069
- Big Nose.
- Watch it!

762
00:51:16,873 --> 00:51:19,501
Whew, that was lucky.

763
00:51:22,712 --> 00:51:24,646
I'm sorry, Reg.

764
00:51:24,714 --> 00:51:26,978
Oh, it's all right.
He's sorry.

765
00:51:27,050 --> 00:51:29,746
He's sorry he led the Fifth Legion
straight to our headquarters.

766
00:51:29,820 --> 00:51:32,687
Well, that's all right,
then, Brian. Sit down.

767
00:51:32,756 --> 00:51:36,317
Have a scone.
Make yourself at home. You klutz!

768
00:51:36,393 --> 00:51:39,851
You stupid, birdbrained,
flat-headed...

769
00:51:39,930 --> 00:51:42,490
[Knocking At Door]

770
00:51:44,634 --> 00:51:47,159
[Indistinct Preaching]

771
00:51:47,237 --> 00:51:50,604
