943
01:01:39,296 --> 01:01:41,594
[Together]
Hail Messiah!

944
01:01:41,665 --> 01:01:44,532
I'm not the Messiah!
Will you please listen?

945
01:01:44,601 --> 01:01:47,900
I'm not the Messiah!
Do you understand? Honestly!

946
01:01:47,971 --> 01:01:52,374
Only the true Messiah
denies his divinity.

947
01:01:52,442 --> 01:01:55,809
