948
01:01:55,879 --> 01:01:58,074
All right,
I am the Messiah!

949
01:01:58,148 --> 01:02:01,879
He is!
He is the Messiah!

950
01:02:01,952 --> 01:02:04,284
Now, fuck off!

951
01:02:12,095 --> 01:02:14,063
