to eat my juniper berries!

954
01:02:19,269 --> 01:02:22,295
You break my bloody foot,
you break my vow of silence...

955
01:02:22,372 --> 01:02:25,398
and then you try to clean up
on my juniper bushes!

956
01:02:25,475 --> 01:02:28,808
- Lay off!
- This is the Messiah, the Chosen One!

957
01:02:28,878 --> 01:02:32,006
- No, he's not.
- An unbeliever!

958
01:02:32,082 --> 01:02:36,246
- An unbeliever!
- Persecute. Kill the heretic!

959
01:02:36,319 --> 01:02:38,753
[Indistinct Shouting]

960
01:02:38,822 --> 01:02:42,258
- Seize him!
- Leave him alone!

961
01:02:42,325 --> 01:02:44,623
Leave him alone!

962
01:02:44,694 --> 01:02:46,958
Leave him alone.

963
01:02:47,030 --> 01:02:49,999
Let him go! Please!

964
01:02:53,970 --> 01:02:56,905
- Brian?
- Judith?

965
01:03:01,645 --> 01:03:04,580
[Mrs. Cohen]
Cock-a-doodle-doo!

966
01:03:43,653 --> 01:03:48,386
Look! There he is!
The Chosen One has woken!

967
01:03:50,894 --> 01:03:53,328
