985
01:04:42,712 --> 01:04:45,272
Brian! Brian!

986
01:04:45,348 --> 01:04:47,441
Right, my lad.
What have you been up to?

987
01:04:47,517 --> 01:04:49,485
- Nothing, Mum.
- Come on, out with it.

988
01:04:49,552 --> 01:04:51,486
Well, they think
I'm the Messiah, Mum.

989
01:04:51,554 --> 01:04:53,920
What have you
been telling them?

990
01:04:53,990 --> 01:04:56,288
- Nothing. I only...
- You're only making it worse for yourself.

991
01:04:56,359 --> 01:04:59,886
- I can explain.
- Let me explain, Mrs. Cohen!

992
01:04:59,963 --> 01:05:02,625
- [Gasps]
- Your son is a born leader.

993
01:05:02,699 --> 01:05:06,362
Those people out there are following him
because they believe in him.

994
01:05:06,436 --> 01:05:09,371
They believe he can give them hope...
hope of a new life,

995
01:05:09,439 --> 01:05:11,907
a new world,
a better future!

996
01:05:14,110 --> 01:05:16,374
- Who's that?
- [Gasps]

997
01:05:16,446 --> 01:05:19,506
That's Judith, Mum.
Judith, Mother.

998
01:05:19,582 --> 01:05:21,516
Hmm. Aaah!

999
01:05:23,253 --> 01:05:27,349
- Ohhh!
- Messiah! Messiah! Messiah!

1000
01:05:27,424 --> 01:05:30,393
Messiah!
Show us the Messiah!

1001
01:05:30,460 --> 01:05:33,691
Now, you listen here.
He's not the Messiah!

1002
01:05:33,763 --> 01:05:37,028
He's a very naughty boy.
Now, go away!

1003
01:05:37,100 --> 01:05:41,161
- Who are you?
- I'm his mother, that's who.

1004
01:05:41,237 --> 01:05:45,697
Behold his mother!
Behold his mother!

1005
01:05:45,775 --> 01:05:49,176
Hail to thee,
mother of Brian!

1006
01:05:49,245 --> 01:05:53,773
Blessed art thou!
Hosanna!

1007
01:05:53,850 --> 01:05:57,479
All praise to thee,
