1008
01:05:57,554 --> 01:06:00,785
Well, now don't think
you can get around me like that.

1009
01:06:00,857 --> 01:06:04,349
He's not coming out,
and that's my final word.

1010
01:06:05,628 --> 01:06:08,495
- Now, shove off!
- No!

1011
01:06:08,565 --> 01:06:13,025
- Did you hear what I said?
- Yes!

1012
01:06:13,102 --> 01:06:16,003
Oh, I see.
It's like that, is it?

1013
01:06:16,072 --> 01:06:19,473
- Yes!
- Oh, all right, then.

1014
01:06:19,542 --> 01:06:23,273
You can see him for one minute,
but not one second more!

1015
01:06:23,346 --> 01:06:25,837
- Do you understand?
- Yes.

1016
01:06:25,915 --> 01:06:30,079
- Promise?
- Well... all right.

1017
01:06:30,153 --> 01:06:33,816
All right, here he is, then.
Come on, Brian. Come and talk.

1018
01:06:33,890 --> 01:06:37,291
- But, Mum, Judith.
- Oh, leave that Welsh tart alone.

1019
01:06:37,360 --> 01:06:39,328
I don't really want to.

1020
01:06:39,395 --> 01:06:42,455
Brian! Brian!
Brian! Brian!

1021
01:06:42,532 --> 01:06:45,831
[Shouting Continues]

1022
01:06:45,902 --> 01:06:49,770
- Good morning.
- A blessing! A blessing!

1023
01:06:49,839 --> 01:06:54,401
No, no. Please.
Please, please listen.

1024
01:06:54,477 --> 01:06:57,776
I've got one or two
things to say.

1025
01:06:57,847 --> 01:07:00,407
Tell us!
Tell us both of them!

1026
01:07:00,483 --> 01:07:03,247
Look, you've
got it all wrong.

1027
01:07:03,319 --> 01:07:05,913
You don't need to follow me.

1028
01:07:05,989 --> 01:07:09,254
You don't need
to follow anybody.

1029
01:07:09,325 --> 01:07:11,657
You've got to think
for yourselves.

1030
01:07:11,728 --> 01:07:14,492
You're all individuals.

1031
01:07:14,564 --> 01:07:17,829
[Together]
Yes, we're all individuals!

1032
01:07:17,901 --> 01:07:19,926
You're all different.

1033
01:07:20,003 --> 01:07:23,166
Yes, we're all different!

1034
01:07:23,239 --> 01:07:25,935
- I'm not.
- Shhh.

1035
01:07:26,009 --> 01:07:29,672
You've all got to work it
out for yourselves.

1036
01:07:29,746 --> 01:07:33,876
Yes, we've got to work it
out for ourselves!

1037
01:07:33,950 --> 01:07:35,941
Exactly.

1038
01:07:36,019 --> 01:07:38,249
Tell us more!

1039
01:07:38,321 --> 01:07:42,849
No! That's the point!
Don't let anyone tell you what to do!

1040
01:07:42,926 --> 01:07:44,951
Otherwise... Ow!

1041
01:07:45,028 --> 01:07:47,053
That's enough.
That's enough.

1042
01:07:47,130 --> 01:07:50,657
