1073
01:09:38,508 --> 01:09:41,272
- Reg has been dominating us for too long.
- Well, yes.

1074
01:09:41,344 --> 01:09:45,144
- It needed saying, and you said it, Brian.
- You're very attractive.

1075
01:09:45,214 --> 01:09:48,479
It's our revolution.
We can all do it together.

1076
01:09:48,551 --> 01:09:51,384
- I think. I think...
- We're all behind you, Brian.

1077
01:09:51,454 --> 01:09:54,548
- The revolution is in your hands!
- What?

1078
01:09:54,624 --> 01:09:56,888
No, that's not
what I meant at all!

1079
01:09:56,959 --> 01:10:00,292
You're fuckin' nicked,
me old beauty.

1080
01:10:00,363 --> 01:10:02,297
Right.

